<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions/j_local_exchange_interaction> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions/j_local_exchange_interaction> rdfs:comment "\n        Value of the exchange interaction. In rotational invariant systems, j_local_exchange_interaction = j_hunds_coupling.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions/j_local_exchange_interaction> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions> .
