<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions/u_interorbital_interaction> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.HubbardInteractions/u_interorbital_interaction> rdfs:comment "\n        Value of the (interorbital) Coulomb interaction. In rotational invariant systems,\n        u_interorbital_interaction = u_interaction - 2 * j_hunds_coupling.\n        " .
