<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.ParticleState/mass> rdfs:comment "\n        Mass associated with this particle/site, in kilograms.\n\n        This is an immutable per-particle descriptor intended for downstream\n        analyses that require per-particle masses.\n        For `AtomsState`, it is the mass of the modeled atomic site (including\n        isotope/effective choices provided by the source data). For `CGBeadState`,\n        it is the bead mass.\n        Method-related mass assignments belong in method-specific sections.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.ParticleState/mass> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.ParticleState> .
