<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> rdfs:comment "\n        Solver algotithm used to diagonalize the BSE Hamiltonian.\n\n        | Name | Description | Reference |\n        | --------- | ----------------------- | ----------- |\n        | `'Full-diagonalization'` | Full diagonalization of the BSE Hamiltonian | - |\n        | `'Lanczos-Haydock'` | Subspace iterative Lanczos-Haydock algorithm | https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.59.5441 |\n        | `'GMRES'` | Generalized minimal residual method | https://doi.org/10.1137/0907058 |\n        | `'SLEPc'` | Scalable Library for Eigenvalue Problem Computations | https://slepc.upv.es/ |\n        | `'TDA'` | Tamm-Dancoff approximation | https://doi.org/10.1016/S0009-2614(99)01149-5 |\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> rdfs:label "solver" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> rdfs:range xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:enumValue "Full-diagonalization" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:enumValue "GMRES" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:enumValue "Lanczos-Haydock" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:enumValue "SLEPc" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:enumValue "TDA" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/solver> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> rdfs:comment "\n        Type of the BSE Hamiltonian solved:\n\n            H_BSE = H_diagonal + 2 * gx * Hx - gc * Hc\n\n        Online resources for the theory:\n        - http://exciting.wikidot.com/carbon-excited-states-from-bse#toc1\n        - https://www.vasp.at/wiki/index.php/Bethe-Salpeter-equations_calculations\n        - https://docs.abinit.org/theory/bse/\n        - https://www.yambo-code.eu/wiki/index.php/Bethe-Salpeter_kernel\n\n        | Name | Description |\n        | --------- | ----------------------- |\n        | `'Singlet'` | gx = 1, gc = 1 |\n        | `'Triplet'` | gx = 0, gc = 1 |\n        | `'IP'` | Independent-particle approach |\n        | `'RPA'` | Random Phase Approximation |\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> rdfs:label "type" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> rdfs:range xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> nomad:enumValue "IP" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> nomad:enumValue "RPA" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> nomad:enumValue "Singlet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> nomad:enumValue "Triplet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BSE/type> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
