<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BaseModelMethod/name> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BaseModelMethod/name> rdfs:comment "\n        Name of the mathematical model. This is typically used to identify the model Hamiltonian used in the\n        simulation. Typical standard names: 'DFT', 'TB', 'GW', 'BSE', 'DMFT', 'NMR', 'kMC'.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BaseModelMethod/name> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.BaseModelMethod> .
