<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/explicit_correlation> rdfs:comment "\n        Explicit correlation treatment.\n        These methods introduce the interelectronic distance coordinate\n        directly into the wavefunction to treat dynamical electron correlation.\n        It can be added linearly (R12) or exponentially (F12).\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/explicit_correlation> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC> .
