<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/perturbative_correction> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/perturbative_correction> rdfs:comment "\n        Label for the perturbative corrections:\n          - '(T)'   : standard perturbative triples\n          - '[T]'   : Brueckner-based or other variant\n          - '(T0)'  : approximate version of (T)\n          - '[T0]'  : approximate, typically for Brueckner references\n          - '(Q)'   : perturbative quadruples, e.g., CCSDT(Q)\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/perturbative_correction> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC> .
