<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/perturbative_correction_order> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.CC/perturbative_correction_order> rdfs:comment "\n        The excitation orders included only in a perturbative manner.\n        For instance, in CCSD(T), singles and doubles are solved iteratively,\n        while triples appear as a perturbative correction => [3].\n        " .
