<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.RelativityModel/approximation> rdfs:comment "\n        Specific approximation or decoupling scheme.\n          • DKH  : Douglas-Kroll-Hess (all orders)\n          • ZORA : Zeroth-order regular approximation      \n          • FORA  : First-order regular approximation\n          • IORA  : Improved regular approximation\n          • X2C  : Exact two-component\n          • BSS  : Barysz-Sadlej-Snijders\n          • NESC: Normalized elimination of the small component (Dyall)\n          • Pauli: Pauli spin-orbit correction\n          • SOMF : Spin-orbit mean-field added after SCF\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.RelativityModel/approximation> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.RelativityModel> .
