<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.XCComponent/range_separation_function> nomad:enumValue "erf" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.XCComponent/range_separation_function> nomad:enumValue "erfc" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.XCComponent/range_separation_function> nomad:enumValue "exp" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.XCComponent/range_separation_function> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
