<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation/origin_shift> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation/origin_shift> nomad:shape "[3]"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation/supercell_matrix> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation/supercell_matrix> rdfs:comment "\n        Specifies the matrix that transforms the primitive unit cell into the supercell in\n        which the actual calculation is performed. In the easiest example, it is a diagonal\n        matrix whose elements multiply the lattice_vectors, e.g., [[3, 0, 0], [0, 3, 0], [0, 0, 3]]\n        is a $3 x 3 x 3$ superlattice.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation/supercell_matrix> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.AlternativeRepresentation> .
