<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem/dimensionality> rdfs:comment "\n        Dimensionality of the system: 0, 1, 2, or 3 dimensions. For atomistic systems this\n        is automatically evaluated by using the topology-scaling algorithm:\n\n            https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevLett.118.106101.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem/dimensionality> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem> .
