<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem/name> rdfs:comment "\n        Any verbose naming refering to the ModelSystem. Can be left empty if it is a simple\n        crystal or it can be filled up. For example, an heterostructure of graphene (G) sandwiched\n        in between hexagonal boron nitrides (hBN) slabs could be named 'hBN/G/hBN'.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem/name> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_system.ModelSystem> .
