<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximated_term> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximated_term> rdfs:comment "\n        The targeted term(s) being approximated. If not provided, it will be\n        inferred from `approximation_type`. For backward compatibility, narrow\n        values are safely widened (e.g., RIJK + 'exchange' → 'jk').\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximated_term> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition> .
