<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximated_term> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximation_type> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximation_type> rdfs:comment "\n        RIJ     : also known as RIJONX, where only Coulomb integrals are approximated.\n        RIJK    : both Coulomb and exchange integrals.\n        RIJCOSX : RIJ for Coulomb and COSX for HF exchange.\n        SENEX   : Similar to COSX, relevant for Turbomole.\n        CD      : Cholesky decomposition of the two-electron integral tensor\n        CD_F12  : Cholesky decomposition specialized for F12/explicit-correlation integrals\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition/approximation_type> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.IntegralDecomposition> .
