<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/all_points> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/all_points> rdfs:comment "\n        Full list of the mesh points without any symmetry operations in units of the `reciprocal_lattice_vectors`. In the\n        presence of symmetry operations, this quantity is a larger list than `points` (as it will contain all the points\n        in the Brillouin zone).\n        " .
