<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/all_points> nomad:shape "['*', 3]"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/center> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/center> rdfs:comment "\n        Identifier for the center of the Mesh:\n\n        | Name      | Description                      |\n        | --------- | -------------------------------- |\n        | `'Gamma-centered'` | Regular mesh is centered around Gamma. No offset. |\n        | `'Monkhorst-Pack'` | Regular mesh with an offset of half the reciprocal lattice vector. |\n        | `'Gamma-offcenter'` | Regular mesh with an offset that is neither `'Gamma-centered'`, nor `'Monkhorst-Pack'`. |\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/center> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh> .
