<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/high_symmetry_points> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/k_line_density> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/k_line_density> rdfs:comment "\n        Amount of sampled k-points per unit reciprocal length along each axis. Contains the least precise density out of all axes.\n        Should only be compared between calculations of similar dimensionality.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh/k_line_density> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh> .
