<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KSpace/reciprocal_lattice_vectors> rdfs:comment "\n        Reciprocal lattice vectors of the simulated cell, in Cartesian coordinates and\n        including the $2 pi$ pre-factor. The first index runs over each lattice vector. The\n        second index runs over the $x, y, z$ Cartesian coordinates.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KSpace/reciprocal_lattice_vectors> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KSpace> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KSpace/reciprocal_lattice_vectors> rdfs:label "reciprocal_lattice_vectors" .
