<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/reference_configuration> rdfs:comment "\n        Electronic configuration used to generate the pseudopotential (e.g., \"3s1 3d0.5\" or \"3p6 3d7 4s1\").\n        Documents the valence electron occupations used during generation.\n        The configuration string may only show the outermost valence orbitals explicitly.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/reference_configuration> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> .
