<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/spin_channel> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/type> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/type> rdfs:comment "\n        Type categorization of the electronic band gap. This quantity is directly related with `momentum_transfer` as by\n        definition, the electronic band gap is `'direct'` for zero momentum transfer (or if `momentum_transfer` is `None`) and `'indirect'`\n        for finite momentum transfer.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/type> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap> .
