<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/type> nomad:enumValue "indirect" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.band_gap.ElectronicBandGap/type> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
