<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.BaseElectronicEigenvalues/n_levels> rdfs:comment "\n        Number of energy levels per sampling point.\n\n        In periodic systems these correspond to electronic bands; in molecular\n        calculations they correspond to (spin-resolved) molecular orbitals or\n        similar one-particle states.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.BaseElectronicEigenvalues/n_levels> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.BaseElectronicEigenvalues> .
