<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/lowest_unoccupied> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/lowest_unoccupied> rdfs:comment "\n        Lowest unoccupied electronic eigenvalue. Together with `highest_occupied`, it defines the\n        electronic band gap.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/lowest_unoccupied> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues> .
