<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> rdfs:comment "\n        Occupation of the electronic eigenvalues. This is a number depending whether the `spin_channel` has been set or not.\n        If `spin_channel` is set, then this number is between 0 and 1, where 0 means that the state is unoccupied and 1 means\n        that the state is fully occupied; if `spin_channel` is not set, then this number is between 0 and 2. The shape of\n        this quantity is defined as `[K.n_points, K.dimensionality, n_levels]`, where `K` is a `variable` which can\n        be `KMesh` or `KLinePath`, depending whether the simulation mapped the whole Brillouin zone or just a specific\n        path.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> rdfs:label "occupation" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> rdfs:range xsd:double .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/occupation> nomad:shape "['*', 'n_levels']"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/spin_channel> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
