<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues/spin_channel> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.electronic_eigenvalues.ElectronicEigenvalues> .
