<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/entity_ref> rdfs:comment "\n        Reference to the `ElectronicState` section describing the correlated orbitals for which the\n        Green's function properties are calculated. The parent AtomsState can be accessed via\n        `entity_ref.get_parent_entity()`.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/entity_ref> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> .
