<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/n_atoms> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/space_id> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/space_id> rdfs:comment "\n        String used to identify the space in which the Green's function property is represented. The spaces are:\n\n        | `space_id` | variable type |\n        | ------ | ------ |\n        | 'r' | WignerSeitz |\n        | 'rt' | WignerSeitz + Time |\n        | 'rw' | WignerSeitz + Frequency |\n        | 'rit' | WignerSeitz + ImaginaryTime |\n        | 'riw' | WignerSeitz + MatsubaraFrequency |\n        | 'k' | KMesh |\n        | 'kt' | KMesh + Time |\n        | 'kw' | KMesh + Frequency |\n        | 'kit' | KMesh + ImaginaryTime |\n        | 'kiw' | KMesh + MatsubaraFrequency |\n        | 't' | Time |\n        | 'it' | Frequency |\n        | 'w' | ImaginaryTime |\n        | 'iw' | MatsubaraFrequency |\n        " .
