<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_class> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_class> rdfs:comment "\n        Role of each MO within a correlated calculation or active-space\n        protocol:\n\n        * core     : energy-frozen doubly-occupied  \n        * inactive : doubly-occupied but variationally optimised  \n        * active   : part of the active space  \n        * virtual  : unoccupied (correlated) orbital  \n        * deleted  : pruned for technical reasons\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_class> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals> .
