<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> rdfs:comment "\n        The AO→MO coefficient matrix **C**, such that \n        ψ_i(r) = ∑_μ C[i,μ] φ_μ(r). \n        Row index i runs over MOs, column index μ runs over AOs in `basis_set_ref`.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> rdfs:label "mo_coefficients" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> rdfs:range xsd:double .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients> nomad:shape "['n_mo', 'n_ao']"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> rdfs:comment "\n        Imaginary component of the AO→MO coefficient matrix **C**. \n        Combine it with `mo_coefficients` to obtain the full complex matrix:\n            C_complex = mo_coefficients + 1j * mo_coefficients_im  \n        Leave this quantity unset (or an empty array) when the wave-function\n        is strictly real, as is typical in non-relativistic calculations without complex basis functions.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> rdfs:label "mo_coefficients_im" .
