<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_coefficients_im> nomad:shape "['n_mo', 'n_ao']"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_energies> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_energies> rdfs:comment "\n        Orbital energies for each MO. In a canonical SCF these are the eigenvalues \n        of the (Fock) Hamiltonian; in correlated frameworks they may be natural-orbital\n        energies or any other chosen set.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_energies> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.molecular_orbitals.MolecularOrbitals/mo_energies> rdfs:label "mo_energies" .
