<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/temperature> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/temperature> rdfs:comment "\n        Temperature at which the chemical potential is calculated.\n        Essential for finite-temperature calculations.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/temperature> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> .
