<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/temperature> nomad:unit "'kelvin'"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/type> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/type> rdfs:comment "\n        Type of chemical potential calculation. Examples: 'electronic', 'atomic',\n        'ionic', 'molecular'. Helps identify what kind of particles this applies to.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/type> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> .
