<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> rdfs:comment "\n        Eigenvalues of the Hessian. Sorted during normalization with positive values\n        descending, followed by zeros, then negative values ascending (most negative\n        first). Very low-magnitude modes in solid-state phonon calculations\n        (e.g., <100 cm-1) or when using RI/DF approximations often reflect numerical\n        artifacts rather than true instabilities.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> rdfs:label "eigenvalues" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> rdfs:range xsd:double .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> nomad:shape "['*']"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/eigenvalues> nomad:unit "'joule / m ** 2'"^^xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> rdfs:comment "\n        Matrix dimension (number of degrees of freedom) of the square Hessian in the\n        coordinate basis used by the parser. For Cartesian atomic Hessians this is\n        typically 3 * N_atoms; constrained/filtered coordinates should use the\n        remaining degrees of freedom.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> rdfs:label "n_hessian_dim" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> rdfs:range <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/datatype/positive_int%28%29> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_hessian_dim> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> rdfs:comment "\n        Number of negative Hessian eigenvalues (imaginary vibrational frequencies).\n        A value of 0 indicates a local minimum, 1 a first-order saddle point, and\n        >1 a higher-order saddle point. Leave unset if the Hessian was evaluated\n        away from a stationary point.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> rdfs:label "n_negative_eigenvalues" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> rdfs:range <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/datatype/positive_int%28%29> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/n_negative_eigenvalues> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> rdfs:comment "\n        Stationary-point classification (requires zero gradient) based on Hessian\n        eigenvalue signs. Use 'saddle_point' for any stationary point with one or\n        more negative eigenvalues (a transition state corresponds to exactly one).\n        Use 'maximum' when all eigenvalues are negative (negative-definite Hessian).\n        Use 'non_stationary' if the Hessian was evaluated where the gradient is\n        non-zero and no stationary point classification applies. Use 'unavailable'\n        when no classification could be determined from the data.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> rdfs:label "stationary_point_type" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> rdfs:range xsd:string .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:enumValue "maximum" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:enumValue "minimum" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:enumValue "non_stationary" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:enumValue "saddle_point" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:enumValue "unavailable" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/stationary_point_type> nomad:propertyKind "quantity" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/value> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/value> rdfs:comment "\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/value> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Hessian/value> rdfs:label "value" .
