<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/coupling_type> nomad:enumValue "anisotropic" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/coupling_type> nomad:enumValue "isotropic" .
