<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/pressure_update_delta> rdf:type owl:DatatypeProperty .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/pressure_update_delta> rdfs:comment "\n        Amount to be added (subtracted if negative) to the current reference_pressure\n        at a frequency of pressure_update_frequency when pressure_profile is \"linear\".\n        The pressure temperature is then replaced by this new value until the next update.\n        " .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/pressure_update_delta> rdfs:domain <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.molecular_dynamics.BarostatParameters/pressure_update_delta> rdfs:label "pressure_update_delta" .
