<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> rdfs:comment "Describes a quantum state under spherical symmetry. Supports SOC and relativistic effects.\n\nThe system is only defined up to the given quantum numbers. States with a wider degeneracy are possible by keeping some quantum numbers undefined.\n\nQuantum number relationships:\n- j and l, s: j = |l - s|, |l - s| + 1, ..., l + s (total angular momentum from orbital and spin coupling)\n- m_j and j: m_j ∈ [-j, -j+1, ..., j-1, j] (azimuthal projection of j, 2j+1 values)\n- m_l and l: m_l ∈ [-l, -l+1, ..., l-1, l] (azimuthal projection of l, 2l+1 values)\n- κ (kappa_quantum_number) is specific to relativistic settings and populates j and l during normalization, not vice versa." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> rdfs:label "SphericalSymmetryState" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.BaseSpinOrbitalState> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/coupling_origin> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/j_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/kappa_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/l_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/mj_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/ml_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/ms_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState/s_quantum_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state.SphericalSymmetryState> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.atoms_state" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> rdf:type owl:Class .
