<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital/energy_parameter_n> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital/energy_status> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital/n_terms> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> rdfs:comment "Collection of all (S)(L)APW and local orbital components that contribute\nto a single $l$-channel. $l$ here stands for the angular momentum parameter\nin the Laplace spherical harmonics $Y_{l, m}$." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> rdfs:label "APWLChannel" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.BasisSetComponent> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel/n_orbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel/name> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel/orbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:hasSubSection <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> rdfs:comment "Implementation of `APWWavefunction` capturing a local orbital extending a foundational APW basis set.\nLocal orbitals allow for flexible additions to an `APWOrbital` specification.\nThey may be included to describe semi-core states, virtual states, ghost bands, or improve overall convergence.\n\n* D. J. Singh and L. Nordström, \"Role of the Linearization Energies,\" in Planewaves, pseudopotentials, and the LAPW method, 2nd ed. New York, NY: Springer, 2006, pp. 49-52." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> rdfs:label "APWLocalOrbital" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLocalOrbital> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> rdfs:comment "Implementation of `APWWavefunction` capturing the foundational (S)(L)APW basis sets, all of the form $\\sum_{lm} \\left[ \\sum_o c_{lmo} rac{\\partial}{\\partial r}u_l(r, \\epsilon_l) \right] Y_lm$.\nThe energy parameter $\\epsilon_l$ is always considered fixed during diagonalization, opposed to the original APW formulation.\nThis representation then has to match the plane-wave $k_n$ points within the muffin-tin sphere.\n\nIts `name` is showcased as `(s)(l)apw: <differential order>`.\n\n* D. J. Singh and L. Nordström, \"INTRODUCTION TO THE LAPW METHOD,\" in Planewaves, pseudopotentials, and the LAPW method, 2nd ed. New York, NY: Springer, 2006, pp. 43-52." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> rdfs:label "APWOrbital" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWBaseOrbital> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital/type> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWOrbital> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:comment "A `PlaneWaveBasisSet` specialized to the APW use case.\nIts main descriptors are defined in terms of the `MuffinTin` regions." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:label "APWPlaneWaveBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet/cutoff_fractional> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWPlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> rdfs:comment "Defines an **atom-centered basis set** for quantum chemistry calculations.\nThese expansions are typically built around each atom's position, using either:\n  - Slater-type orbitals (STO)\n  - Gaussian-type orbitals (GTO)\n  - Numerical atomic orbitals (NAO)\n  - Effective-core potentials or point-charges (PC, cECP, etc.)\n\nThis section may reference multiple `AtomCenteredFunction` objects, each describing\na single contracted function or shell. Additionally, one can label the overall\nbasis set name (e.g., \"cc-pVTZ\", \"def2-SVP\", \"6-31G**\") and specify the high-level\nrole of the basis set in the calculation.\n\n**Common examples**:\n  - **Pople basis** (3-21G, 6-31G(d), 6-311++G(2df,2pd), etc.)\n  - **Dunning correlation-consistent** (cc-pVDZ, cc-pVTZ, aug-cc-pVTZ, etc.)\n  - **Slater basis** used in ADF, for instance\n  - **ECP** (Effective Core Potential) expansions like LANL2DZ or SDD for transition metals\n\n**References**:\n  - F. Jensen, *Introduction to Computational Chemistry*, 2nd ed., Wiley (2007).\n  - A. Szabo, N. S. Ostlund, *Modern Quantum Chemistry*, McGraw-Hill (1989).\n  - T. H. Dunning Jr., J. Chem. Phys. 90, 1007 (1989) for correlation-consistent basis sets." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> rdfs:label "AtomCenteredBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.BasisSetComponent> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/ao_custom_order> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/ao_ordering_convention> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/basis_set> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/n_total_basis_functions> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/role> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/type> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/atomic_orbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/ecps> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet/functional_compositions> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:hasSubSection <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:hasSubSection <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomicOrbitals> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:hasSubSection <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.EffectiveCorePotential> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredBasisSet> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> rdfs:comment "Specifies a single contracted basis function in an atom-centered basis set.\n\nIn many quantum-chemistry codes, an atom-centered basis set is composed of\nseveral \"shells,\" each shell containing one or more basis functions of a certain\nangular momentum. For instance, a shell of p-type orbitals (ℓ=1) typically\nconsists of 3 degenerate functions (p_x, p_y, p_z) if `harmonic_type='cartesian'`\nor 3 spherical harmonics if `harmonic_type='spherical'`.\n\nA single \"atom-centered function\" can be a linear combination of multiple\nprimitive Gaussians (or Slater-type orbitals, STOs).\nIn practice, these contract together to form the final basis function used by\nthe SCF or post-SCF method. Often, each contraction is labeled by its\nangular momentum (e.g., s, p, d, f) and a set of exponents and coefficients.\n\n**References**:\n  - T. Helgaker, P. Jørgensen, J. Olsen, *Molecular Electronic-Structure Theory*, Wiley (2000).\n  - F. Jensen, *Introduction to Computational Chemistry*, 2nd ed., Wiley (2007).\n  - J. B. Foresman, Æ. Frisch, *Exploring Chemistry with Electronic Structure Methods*, Gaussian Inc." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> rdfs:label "AtomCenteredFunction" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction/angular_momentum> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.AtomCenteredFunction/angular_type> .
