<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.MuffinTinRegion> nomad:hasSubSection <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.APWLChannel> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.MuffinTinRegion> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.MuffinTinRegion" .
