<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:comment "Basis set over a reciprocal mesh, where each point $k_n$ represents a planar-wave basis function $rac{1}{\\sqrt{\\omega}} e^{i k_n r}$.\nTypically the grid itself is cartesian with only points within a designated sphere considered.\nThe cutoff radius may be defined by a reciprocal length, or more commonly, the equivalent kinetic energy for a free particle.\n\n* D. J. Singh and L. Nordström, \"Why Planewaves\" in Planewaves, pseudopotentials, and the LAPW method, 2nd ed. New York, NY: Springer, 2006, pp. 24-26." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:label "PlaneWaveBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.BasisSetComponent> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet/cutoff_energy> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet/cutoff_radius> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set.PlaneWaveBasisSet> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.basis_set" .
