<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound> rdfs:comment "Bounds checker for numeric values using mathematical interval notation.\n`None` and `NaN` values are allowed and will simply pass the checks.\n\nRange specification:\n    - '[0,1]': Closed interval, 0 ≤ x ≤ 1\n    - '(0,1)': Open interval, 0 < x < 1\n    - '[0,1)': Half-open interval, 0 ≤ x < 1\n    - '[1,)': Lower bounded, x ≥ 1\n    - '(,10]': Upper bounded, x ≤ 10\n    - '': Unbounded (-∞, ∞)" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound> rdfs:label "Bound" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.Bound> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.data_types.m_float_bounded> rdf:type owl:Class .
