<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.CosineAngle> rdfs:comment "Section containing information about a Cosine angle potential:\n$V(\\theta) = \\frac{1}{2} k_\\theta \\left[ \\cos(\\theta) - \\cos(\\theta_0) \\right]^2 + C$,\nwhere $k_\\theta$ is the `force_constant` and $\\theta_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of\nthe angle $\\theta$. $C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.CosineAngle> rdfs:label "CosineAngle" .
