<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.CubicBond> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.CubicBond> rdfs:comment "Section containing information about a Cubic bond potential:\n$V(r) = \\frac{1}{2} k_r (r - r_0)^2 + \\frac{1}{3} k_c (r - r_0)^3 + C$,\nwhere $k_r$ is the (harmonic) `force_constant`, $k_c$ is the `force_constant_cubic`,\nand $r_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of $r$.\nC is an arbitrary constant (not stored)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.CubicBond> rdfs:label "CubicBond" .
