<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.FeneBond> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.FeneBond> rdfs:comment "Section containing information about a FENE potential:\n$V(r) = -\\frac{1}{2} k R_0^2 \\ln \\left[ 1 - \\left( \\frac{r - r_0}{R_0} \\right)^2 \\right] + C$,\n$k$ is the `force_constant`, $r_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of $r$, and $R_0$ is the\nmaximum allowable bond extension beyond $r_0$. $C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.FeneBond> rdfs:label "FeneBond" .
