<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.ForceField> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.ForceField> rdfs:comment "Section containing the parameters of a (classical, particle-based) force field model.\nTypical `numerical_settings` are ForceCalculations and ParticleParametersContainer.\nLists of interactions by type and, if available, corresponding parameters can be given\nwithin `interactions`.\nAdditionally, a published model can be referenced with `reference`." .
