<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.ForceField> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.ForceField/contributions> .
