<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngle> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngle> rdfs:comment "Section containing information about a Harmonic angle potential:\n$V(\\theta) = \\frac{1}{2} k_\\theta (\\theta - \\theta_0)^2 + C$,\nwhere $k_\\theta$ is the `force_constant` and $\\theta_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of\nthe angle $\\theta$. $C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngle> rdfs:label "HarmonicAngle" .
