<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngle> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling> rdfs:comment "Harmonic form of an angle–dihedral coupling potential:\n$V = k_1(\\theta - \\theta_0)^2 + k_2(\\phi - \\phi_0)^2 + k_3(\\theta - \\theta_0)(\\phi - \\phi_0)$" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling> rdfs:label "HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.AngleDihedralCouplingPotential> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.HarmonicAngleDihedralCoupling" .
