<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.PolynomialPotential> rdfs:comment "Abstract class for potentials with polynomial form:\n$V(x) = [\\left k_1 (x - x_0) + k_2 (x - x_0)^2 + x_3 (x - x_0)^3 + \\dots + C$,\nwhere $\\{x_1, x_2, x_3 \\dots}$ are the `force_constants` for each term in the polynomial\nexpression and $x_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of $x$. $C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored).\nThis class is intended to be used with another class specifying the potential type, e.g., BondPotential, AnglePotential, etc." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.PolynomialPotential> rdfs:label "PolynomialPotential" .
