<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.TabulatedPotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.TabulatedPotential/forces> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.TabulatedPotential> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.TabulatedPotential" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.TabulatedPotential> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> rdfs:comment "Section containing information about a Urey-Bradley angle potential:\n$V(\\theta) = \\frac{1}{2} k_\\theta (\\theta - \\theta_0)^2 +\n\\frac{1}{2} k_{13} (r_{13} - r_{13}^0)^2 + C$,\nwhere where $k_\\theta$ is the `force_constant` and $\\theta_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of\nthe angle $\\theta$, as for a harmonic angle potential. $k_{13}$ is the `force_constant_UB`\nfor the 1-3 term, and $r_{13}^0$ is the `equilibrium_value_UB` of the 1-3 distance (i.e.,\nthe distance between the edge particles forming the 1-2-3 angle, $\\theta$), $r_{13}$.\n$C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> rdfs:label "UreyBradleyAngle" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.AnglePotential> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle/equilibrium_value_UB> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle/force_constant_UB> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field.UreyBradleyAngle> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.force_field" .
