<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.model_method.ModelMethodElectronic> rdfs:comment "A base section used to define the parameters of a model Hamiltonian used in electronic structure\ncalculations (TB, DFT, GW, BSE, DMFT, etc)." .
