<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath/high_symmetry_path_values> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath/n_line_points> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath/points> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KLinePath> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.KMesh> rdfs:comment "A base section used to specify the settings of a sampling mesh in reciprocal space. The `points` and other\nk-space quantities are defined in units of the reciprocal lattice vectors, so that to obtain their Cartesian coordinates\nvalue, one should multiply them by the reciprocal lattice vectors (`points_cartesian = points @ reciprocal_lattice_vectors`)." .
