<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.NumericalSettings> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.NumericalSettings" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.NumericalSettings> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.PPCutoff> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.PPCutoff> rdfs:comment "A single plane-wave cutoff recommendation for a pseudopotential, specifying context metadata\nsuch as which physical expansion it controls (wavefunction, charge density, etc.) and its precision\n(package recommendation, library tier, or range bound)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.PPCutoff> rdfs:label "PPCutoff" .
