<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> rdfs:comment "Section containing high-level metadata (type, cutoff energy, XC functional) that identifies which pseudopotential was used.\nPseudopotentials approximate the potential of core electrons and the nucleus, enabling\nefficient treatment of valence electrons in plane-wave codes.\n\nThe actual numerical pseudopotential data (radial functions, projectors, augmentation charges)\nis typically stored in external files which are not parsed into the archive due to size and licensing constraints.\n\nNote: This class is distinct from `EffectiveCorePotential` in basis_set.py, which stores\nanalytical ECP representations for quantum chemistry codes with Gaussian basis sets. ECPs\ncannot represent PAW or ultrasoft pseudopotentials used in plane-wave calculations." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> rdfs:label "Pseudopotential" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.NumericalSettings> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/is_gw_optimized> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/is_norm_conserving> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/l_max> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/lm_max> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.Pseudopotential/n_valence_electrons> .
