<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.SelfConsistency> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.SelfConsistency/threshold_change> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.SelfConsistency> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.numerical_settings.SelfConsistency/threshold_change_unit> .
