<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> rdfs:comment "A base class used to define shared commonalities between Green's function-related properties. This is the case for `ElectronicGreensFunction`,\n`ElectronicSelfEnergy`, `HybridizationFunction` in DMFT simulations.\n\nThese physical properties are matrices matrix represented in different spaces. These spaces can be:\n`WignerSeitz` (real space), `KMesh`, `MatsubaraFrequency`, `Frequency`, `Time`, or `ImaginaryTime`.\nFor example, G(k, ω) will have corresponds to `k_mesh` and `real_frequency` being set.\n\nThe `entity_ref` field points to an `ElectronicState` describing the correlated orbitals. To access the\nparent AtomsState, use `entity_ref.get_parent_entity()`. This follows the ElectronicState gateway pattern.\n\nFurther information in M. Wallerberger et al., Comput. Phys. Commun. 235, 2 (2019)." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> rdfs:label "BaseGreensFunction" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.physical_property.PhysicalProperty> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/entity_ref> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/local_model_type> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/n_atoms> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/space_id> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/spin_channel> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/imaginary_time> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/k_mesh> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/subsection/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.greens_function.BaseGreensFunction/matsubara_frequency> .
