<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> rdfs:comment "Free energy cost of adding or extracting a particle from a thermodynamic system.\n\nAt finite temperature, the chemical potential determines the equilibrium condition\nfor particle exchange between different phases or subsystems. It can be defined\nas the partial derivative of the internal energy with respect to particle number\nat constant entropy and volume, or equivalently as the partial derivative of\nthe Gibbs free energy with respect to particle number at constant temperature\nand pressure." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> rdfs:label "ChemicalPotential" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.energies.BaseEnergy> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/fermi_energy> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/particle_number> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/temperature> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential/type> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.ChemicalPotential" .
