<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Enthalpy> rdfs:comment "The total heat content of a system, defined as 'InternalEnergy' + 'Pressure' * 'Volume'." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Enthalpy> rdfs:label "Enthalpy" .
