<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Enthalpy> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Enthalpy" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Enthalpy> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> rdf:type owl:Class .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> rdfs:comment "A measure of the disorder or randomness in a system.\n\nFrom a thermodynamic perspective, `Entropy` is a measure of the system's energy\ndispersal at a specific temperature, and can be interpreted as the unavailability of\na system's thermal energy for conversion into mechanical work. For a reversible\nprocess, the change in `Entropy` is given mathematically by an integral over the\ninfinitesimal `Heat` (i.e., thermal energy transfered into the system) divided by the\n`Temperature`.\n\nFrom a statistical mechanics viewpoint, entropy quantifies the number of microscopic\nconfigurations (microstates) that correspond to a thermodynamic system's macroscopic\nstate, as given by the Boltzmann equation for entropy." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> rdfs:label "Entropy" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.physical_property.PhysicalProperty> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy/value> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy" .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.Entropy> nomad:pythonModule "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics" .
