<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.GibbsFreeEnergy> rdfs:comment "The energy available to do work in a system at constant temperature and pressure,\ngiven by `Enthalpy` - `Temperature` * `Entropy`." .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.properties.thermodynamics.GibbsFreeEnergy> rdfs:label "GibbsFreeEnergy" .
