<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.general.WorkflowConvergenceResults> nomad:definesProperty <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/quantity/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.general.WorkflowConvergenceResults/is_reached> .
<https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.general.WorkflowConvergenceResults> nomad:pythonClass "nomad_simulations.schema_packages.workflow.general.WorkflowConvergenceResults" .
